%% GRAPH 1 — Core Loop (What VibeCat Does)
%% ============================================================

flowchart LR
    OBSERVE["👀 OBSERVE\nWatch screen via\nGemini Live Vision"]
    SUGGEST["💬 SUGGEST\nSpeak up proactively\nbefore user asks"]
    WAIT["⏳ WAIT\nUser confirms\nor declines"]
